gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1beb3da18cf98084490bfbd3dbfc0da071d43b","tid":1921561,"uid":155926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14de36823689d98bc094b3c8c52d4e8d7edab72","tid":1921561,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b8feed4f346549132b5e104ace4070bdf798c6","tid":1921561,"uid":281528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"P牌靠大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各手足起碼要有心理準備<br />\n然後繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"麻麻地 對家私刑我都信<br />\n手足捉狗酷刑我就覺得唔太可能發生"},{"pid":"438e76cf65ac82d4fd03357fb1bdbf596d0454ce","tid":1921561,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c6bbb489153304bdfc63187551247c4c832158","tid":1921561,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b6ec72e6d054c8a01cf98eeab5c49f259734cee","tid":1921561,"uid":281528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e14de36823689d98bc094b3c8c52d4e8d7edab72","tid":1921561,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b8feed4f346549132b5e104ace4070bdf798c6","tid":1921561,"uid":281528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"P牌靠大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各手足起碼要有心理準備<br />\n然後繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"麻麻地 對家私刑我都信<br />\n手足捉狗酷刑我就覺得唔太可能發生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:33:58.000Z","msg":"我睇篇文覺得重點係<br />\n我地討論咁多戰略上同抗爭手法上既問題之後<br />\n最終極一個考驗就係酷刑<br />\n<br />\n唔講我地向狗施加酷刑<br />\n齋諗我地要點面對狗既酷刑已經係必須"},{"pid":"4051cca9efdba8c79413a51faa2f4c661c9d07ad","tid":1921561,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ae40963f29163a8f998e9f7ea2d9e74733dff9b","tid":1921561,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:36:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02699286d552a17fbf9176d082bad6c0be6305bd","tid":1921561,"uid":26161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f616f51e43e56bd14b37bf5f17272e807cc6a5","tid":1921561,"uid":269481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e14de36823689d98bc094b3c8c52d4e8d7edab72","tid":1921561,"uid":325757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b8feed4f346549132b5e104ace4070bdf798c6","tid":1921561,"uid":281528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"P牌靠大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各手足起碼要有心理準備<br />\n然後繼續抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"麻麻地 對家私刑我都信<br />\n手足捉狗酷刑我就覺得唔太可能發生"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:38:04.000Z","msg":"我相信手足捉狗酷刑係遲早一定會發生，甚至可能依家就發生緊<br />\n既然炸彈都有，咁有人殺狗捉狗其實係好合理<br />\n就算真係發生緊，警狗唔會敢公佈。一搞到全世界都知狗隊就玩完架啦，有幾多隻狗抱住必死心態打呢場仗？佢地只係城管黎架咋，打份工架咋，唔會同個政權搵命搏架"}]}